column2: SELECT p.ObjID, p.ra, p.dec, p.petroRad_r, s.z as redshift, g.oh_p5#, g.bptclass, g.lgm_tot_p5# as logMass, g.sfr_tot_p5# as logSFR, p.petroR9#_r, p.petroR5#_r, z.spiral, z.elliptical, z.uncertain INTO masssize FROM SpecObj s, Galaxy p, galSpecExtra g, ZooSpec z WHERE p.ObjID = s.BestObjID AND g.SpecObjID = s.SpecObjID AND z.SpecObjID = s.SpecObjID AND p.clean = # AND s.zWarning = #
